      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t我建议再把这个电影拿出来复习一下，<br/>\n<br/>\n还有静静的顿河等等，<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOGIxOTk0OGI2ZjVlODg3YWNmNDQ4LmpwZz93aWR0aD00OTkmaGVpZ2h0PTM0Ng\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8b19948b6f5e887acf448.jpg?width=499&amp;height=346\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8b19948b6f5e887acf448.jpg?width=499&amp;height=346\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/8b19948b6f5e887acf448.jpg?width=499&amp;height=346\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n这两群人是要把下一代的血流干才罢休（就像俄国内战一样）<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvN2IwNTc3OGE4YTg2MzI5Nzg3ZTg4LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDAwJmhlaWdodD00MjA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7b05778a8a86329787e88.jpg?width=1000&amp;height=420\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7b05778a8a86329787e88.jpg?width=1000&amp;height=420\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7b05778a8a86329787e88.jpg?width=1000&amp;height=420\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODYxY2Y3OWRjMGViOWNmYTNhODllLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDAwJmhlaWdodD00MjA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/861cf79dc0eb9cfa3a89e.jpg?width=1000&amp;height=420\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/861cf79dc0eb9cfa3a89e.jpg?width=1000&amp;height=420\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/861cf79dc0eb9cfa3a89e.jpg?width=1000&amp;height=420\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n我在2022年初已经思考过了，已经伤感过了。那些漂亮的男孩少年，大部分会被送到绞肉机里去的，就像那首歌说的一样（极端讽刺的就是，这首歌一开始的启发就是现在乌克兰的前线，一百多年前）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly95b3V0dS5iZS9aZ1hOVkE5bmd4OD9zaT1GZlNvQ0hSNWRSY1A3VmZKJnQ9MjA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://youtu.be/ZgXNVA9ngx8?si=FfSoCHR5dRcP7VfJ&amp;t=20\">Where Have All the Flowers Gone</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTg4OTllODczYjg4MTQxMTViODUzLmpwZz93aWR0aD02NDAmaGVpZ2h0PTM2MA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/98899e873b8814115b853.jpg?width=640&amp;height=360\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/98899e873b8814115b853.jpg?width=640&amp;height=360\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/98899e873b8814115b853.jpg?width=640&amp;height=360\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
